### âœ… 2. Power Design Recommendations

ğŸ”Œ A. Dual Power Supply Model (Safe & Efficient)

Path	Supply Method	What It Powers

ğŸ”‹ Power Path A	2x 18650 Li-ion (7.4V) + Buck Converter to 5V	Arduino, DFPlayer, GPS, sensors
ğŸ”‹ Power Path B	Separate 3.7V Li-ion + AMS1117 or LM2596 to 4.0V	SIM800L
ğŸ”Œ NodeMCU	USB power bank or same 5V output (min 2A)	NodeMCU & ESP32-CAM


> âš ï¸ Keep SIM800L and ESP32-CAM on isolated regulators to avoid brownouts during high draw (SIM startup, camera init).




